%Let $\mathcal{G} \to M$ be an LGB over a smooth manifold $M$, and $\mathcal{P} \stackrel{\pi}{\to} M$ a principal $\mathcal{G}$-bundle. A \textbf{physical gauge transformation $\tau$} is an element of $\Gamma(\mathcal{G})$.
