-\mleft( \mathcal{r}_\sigma^!A \mright)\mleft( \mleft[ X^h, Y^h\mright] \mright)
	- r_{\sigma}^*\mleft(\mleft(\pi^! \Delta \sigma \mright) \mleft(\mleft[ X^h, Y^h\mright]\mright)\mright)
\\
